INSERT INTO `announcements` VALUES (1,26,'System Maintenance Notice','To provide better service experience, the system will undergo routine maintenance from 2:00-6:00 AM this Saturday. Some functions may be affected during this period. Please prepare accordingly.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(2,26,'New Feature Launch Announcement','We are excited to announce that our new intelligent recommendation feature is now live! This feature will recommend the most relevant content and services based on your usage patterns.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(3,26,'Security Alert Notice','We have recently discovered fraudsters impersonating our customer service representatives. Please be vigilant. Official customer service will never ask for your passwords or verification codes.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(4,26,'Holiday Schedule Update','Please note that our customer service hours will be adjusted during the upcoming holiday period. We will be operating with reduced hours from December 24th to January 2nd.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(5,26,'Privacy Policy Update','We have updated our Privacy Policy to better protect your personal information and comply with the latest regulations. Please review the changes at your earliest convenience.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(6,26,'Server Upgrade Completion','We are pleased to announce that our server upgrade has been successfully completed. Users should experience improved performance and faster loading times across all platforms.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(7,26,'Mobile App Update Available','A new version of our mobile application is now available for download. This update includes bug fixes, performance improvements, and new user interface enhancements.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(8,26,'Community Guidelines Reminder','We want to remind all users to follow our community guidelines. Respectful communication and appropriate content sharing help maintain a positive environment for everyone.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(9,26,'Data Backup Notification','As part of our commitment to data security, we will be performing a comprehensive backup of all user data this weekend. No action is required from users during this process.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(10,26,'Beta Testing Program Launch','We are launching a beta testing program for selected users to try our upcoming features before public release. If you are interested in participating, please contact our support team.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(11,26,'Payment System Enhancement','Our payment system has been enhanced with additional security measures and new payment options. These improvements will provide a more secure and convenient transaction experience.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(12,26,'Terms of Service Update','We have made updates to our Terms of Service to clarify certain provisions and add new service features. The updated terms will take effect 30 days from this announcement.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(13,26,'Customer Satisfaction Survey','We value your feedback! Please take a few minutes to complete our customer satisfaction survey. Your responses will help us improve our services and better meet your needs.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-19 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(14,26,'Network Infrastructure Upgrade','We are upgrading our network infrastructure to provide faster and more reliable service. The upgrade will be performed in phases to minimize service disruption.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-19 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(15,26,'New Partnership Announcement','We are excited to announce our new partnership with leading technology providers. This collaboration will bring enhanced features and services to our platform.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-19 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(16,26,'Account Security Enhancement','We have implemented additional security measures to protect your account. Two-factor authentication is now available and highly recommended for all users.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-05-19 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(17,26,'Service Expansion Notice','We are pleased to announce the expansion of our services to new regions. Users in these areas can now access our full range of features and support services.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-04-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(18,26,'Technical Support Hours Extension','Good news! We are extending our technical support hours to better serve our global user base. Support will now be available 24/7 through multiple channels.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-04-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(19,26,'Platform Performance Report','We are happy to report that our platform has achieved 99.9% uptime this quarter. We continue to invest in infrastructure improvements to maintain this high level of reliability.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-04-26 12:00:00','2025-06-12 09:07:04'),(20,26,'User Training Webinar Series','Join our upcoming webinar series designed to help users maximize their experience with our platform. Sessions will cover advanced features, best practices, and Q&A opportunities.','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-06-12 21:07:04','2025-